org.franca.core.typesystem

Class ActualType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.franca.core.typesystem.ActualType

  • public class ActualType
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a wrapper for the Franca FTypeRef class used by Franca's type system. It takes into account if the referenced type is an implicit array type.
